title: *Sydney Summoners we are looking for volunteers for Summoners' Society Sydney team*

embed.description: Hello Summoners, We are looking for Sydney volunteers team members that would like to gain experience in event management. You will be helping run and put together league of legends events around Sydney.

body:
Hello Summoners, 

Summoners' Society is looking for Sydney Volunteers Team Members. We are looking for people that want to gain experience in event management. We have some really amazing events coming up next year! Great time to get involved with the team.

Apply below, get involved in the amazing community & the SumSoc Team!!
